.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-GRAPH-CONNECTIVITY-STATS" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-graph-connectivity-stats \- FEAT-2164 verb
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-graph-connectivity-stats
.SH DESCRIPTION
verb for lightning CLI (FEAT-2164).
.PP
Returns statistics on node connections from the network graph, including totals for nodes with addresses and aliases. Output: JSON from CLN.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
